Hello, This is my first tut on mopar so im kinda nervous. 
This tut is for rs2hd but if there are any other bases besides rs2hd then this should still work but i only tested on this base so bare with me.
Now the files we will be editing will be one and ONLY one so i will rate this 0.000001/100.
Now, goto [code]Your Source\src\com\rs2hd\packethandler[/code] and look for          [code]ItemPacketHandler[/code]
Open it then look for [code]if (UseWith(2368,2366,usedWith,itemUsed)) {
player.getSmithing().DragonSquaresmithing(player);
}[/code] and under that add this
[code]//Arcane
if (UseWith(13736,13746,usedWith,itemUsed)) {
